column4: I'm currently 24 years old, and I'm a Country Financial Representative. I've been doing insurance for almost 5 years now, and to me it's more than just selling insurance. I got into the insurance industry to take care of people. I want to make sure families are taken care of properly, and to be done in a professional way knowing they can trust and count on me as an advisor, friend and as someone who will go above and beyond for them. I want to help my clients achieve and realize their goals, and that's what drives me every day to do the very best for every client!
Support The Kid for Cancer Inc.
State Farm Insurance- Amy Martinez Agency
Just want to make a difference in kids' lives.
